teal.field

Interface Vector3dField

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    BField, CompositeField, EField, Field, GField, PField, Potential, UnitField

    public interface Vector3dField
    Simple specification for any field of 3D double data, which is accessed through a location within the field.
    Version:
    $Revision: 1.6 $
    Author:
    mesrob, Andrew McKinney, Phil Bailey, Michael Danziger
